OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784198903
OL,3,CDairy farmer says hot weather is
OL,4,Creducing milk production
OL,6,FA Wiltshire dairy farmer has told ITV
OL,7,FNews that this summer's hot weather
OL,8,Fhas reduced milk production, putting
OL,9,Fthe farming industry under further
OL,10,Fpressure.
OL,12,FCeri Cryer, who runs Brinkworth Dairy
OL,13,Fin Chippenham, said she is already
OL,14,Fhaving to feed her herd winter silage
OL,15,Fbecause of a shortage of grass caused
OL,16,Fby the dry conditions and lack of
OL,17,Frainfall.
OL,19,FShe said the hot weather is also
OL,20,Fimpacting the herd's ability to
OL,21,Fproduce milk.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
