FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784198903
OL,3,CDairy farmer says hot weather is
OL,4,Creducing milk production
OL,6,F"The cows are producing less milk. Per
OL,7,Fcow, they're producing about four
OL,8,Flitres less, per cow, per day," Ms
OL,9,FCryer said.
OL,11,F"With our herd size, that represents
OL,12,Faround #1,000, that we're losing per
OL,13,Fweek in milk yield."
OL,15,FShe said the extreme heat has also
OL,16,Freduced the amount of time the cows
OL,17,Fcan be out grazing in the fields.
OL,19,FMs Cryer said there was not a lot of
OL,20,Fmoisture in the ground, which had
OL,21,Fimpacted the grass.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784198903
OL,3,CDairy farmer says hot weather is
OL,4,Creducing milk production
OL,6,F"The grass isn't growing," she said.
OL,7,F"The ground is so dry, so we are
OL,8,Fhaving to feed the silage to the cows."
OL,10,F"This is more expensive, and it also
OL,11,Fmeans that we're running out of our
OL,12,Fwinter feed. It is a huge pressure on
OL,13,Four system."
OL,15,FMs Cryer said she is trying her best
OL,16,Fto protect the farm for the future,
OL,17,Ffor example, by planting new trees to
OL,18,Fcreate shade, but she might have to
OL,19,Fmake some tough business decisions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1784198903
OL,3,CDairy farmer says hot weather is
OL,4,Creducing milk production
OL,6,FShe said: "I just wonder, does this
OL,7,Fnow mean we can't keep as many cows,
OL,8,Fso we're going to have to reduce our
OL,9,Fherd size?
OL,11,F"This means that our area of land,
OL,12,Fbecause of climate change, can produce
OL,13,Fless food for humans. If we've got
OL,14,Fless cows, we're making less milk.
OL,15,FWe're making less cheese.
OL,17,F"It's always tough in farming, but
OL,18,Fit's really tough at the moment."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
